OF - Absorption PRO (Clean & Smart)Ultra-clean, high-precision absorption reversal strategy.Detects institutional buying/selling pressure using volume-weighted delta proxy and VWAP deviation zones.Smart RSI + early-session range filter automatically separates valid range-bound reversals from trend exhaustion.Green/Red circles → High-probability entries (fully tradable)
