OF - Absorption PRO (Clean & Smart)

Ultra-clean, high-precision absorption reversal strategy.Detects institutional buying/selling pressure using volume-weighted delta proxy and VWAP deviation zones.Smart RSI + early-session range filter automatically separates valid range-bound reversals from trend exhaustion.


Green/Red circles → High-probability entries (fully tradable)

Small crosses + colored zones → Rejected signals (avoid)

Blue dotted lines → Session range ±100% deviation levels (optional)



By default: only signals and rejection zones displayed — zero clutter.Minimalist, professional, and deadly accurate on futures & forex (1m–15m).Less noise. Better trades.


